phrases: TL Note: Hitsumabushi: Eel-and-rice bowl, a specialty of Nagoya.
TL Note: A parody of Calpis Water, a Japanese uncarbonated soft drink.
Text in book: Jin is an idiot
TL Note: When the sun goddess Amaterasu was hiding in a cave, Yasakani no Magatama was the kind of jewel that the gods hung on a tree to lure her out.
TL Note: Zashikiwarashi: A type of Japanese ghost that stays in someone is house.
I did it for your sake!
So I did it for you, thinking that you would be happy!
If you are there, answer me.
I do not even want to talk to you!
I am going to open it.
Hey, do not force it closed!
You too, do not open it without my permission!
This will be my territory from today on!
Do you know how hurt and betrayed I feel?
I am going to live here from now on.
I am never going to come out.
I will stock up on Oishinbou.
How many days worth of that did you bring in there?
You will have trouble with the toilet and such.
And do not do it there!
You were so loud that you made me drop my Oishinbou!
You are blaming that on me?
A person cannot possibly live in a closet.
I am not a person; I am a god.
I will show you that I can overcome this hardship.
I am going to do my homework!
These are fried vegetables and eggs.
I am sorry for bothering you every week lately.
She is hiding in the closet because of that?
Yesterday she kept whining and throwing a tantrum.
It is your fault after all.
I have heard all about it.
I know that Jin was mean, but he has apologized.
Why do not you forgive him?
Of all things, he had to do that while I was taking a bath...
It is true that it was thoughtlessness on his part...
Besides, staying in the closet too long is bad for your eyes.
You do not need to worry about that.
A stick that is useful even in the dark.
But it is not healthy if you do not get sunlight.
You will also get thirsty if you shut yourself in, right?
I told you not to worry.
I have my Oishinbou and Capilus.
Why would you tell such an obvious lie?!
Are you an elementary school student?!
With these, I can fight for another ten years.
This time, I will talk to her alone.
Who cares if she does not come out.
You are the because of all this.
If Nagi-san does not come out, you cannot use the closet, right?
It is not like there is anything important...
See, what did I tell you?
All of them have big tits.
Anyway, wait in the other room.
You have to apologize when she comes out.
Jin is not here, so let us have a girl-to-girl talk.
My resolution is as strong as the Curved Jewels of Yasakani.
If the same thing was done to me, I would get mad too.
We need some kind of mental preparation too, right?
What is even more irritating is that he did not spare a thought for my feelings!
Well, it was not that bad...
If not for what happened last night...
I would have been able to accept Jin!
What he did yesterday is unforgivable!
If only it had happened on another day...
Because of your own selfish ideas, you toyed with a woman's innocence, you beast!
What did you go talk to her for?
It is natural that she would get mad.
Frankly, your recklessness is so great that you do not even fear gods.
Well, I know that is true...
But I did it thinking that she would be happy.
You need to follow the necessary procedures for something like this.
Well, I have had similar experiences before.
Anyway, I am counting on you.
I will get ready and head over to your place.
He said he will come over later.
It is been a long time...
I have been pretty busy since she came here.
Oh, my sister is doing something like that?
No wonder the house felt so quiet today.
The two of us are alone, right?
So, Jin-kun, shall I help you drag Neesama out of there?
You think I will fall for that?
Even if you try to lure me out with sweet words, things will not go your way!
She lacks understanding, so just leave her alone.
But now that you have become a closet princess, anyone outside is none of your concern, right?
I have no more interest in the secular world.
Jin-kun, you should forget about Neesama.
Let me take care of you from now on.
Let us do a lot of fun and embarrassing things.
It is too embarrassing to say.
What are you thinking of doing?!
Oh well, let us not bother about the imaginary voices, let us do a lot of embarrassing things now!
Even if it is just a ploy, they are going too far!
You are trying to arouse my interest and drag me out while I am peeking, right?
I will not fall for your trick!
Zange-chan, is not this just an act?
No, you must not say that!
Whether she gets suspicious or not, is this for real?
Let us change this into a documentary.
This is a non-fiction story based on existing people and organizations.
There might be a portrayal of extreme scenes.
If we do not get serious, Neesama will not come out!
Do not take me for a fool!
If I get tricked by your acts and come out, you will say gotcha and catch me, right?!
Jin-kun, look at how much you have discharged.
I am sorry, I got too engrossed in the act.
I cannot answer the phone at the moment.
Please leave your message after the tone.
If I had not stopped them then...
Was not it a pity, Jin-kun?
What do you mean by that?!
Maybe if we got here sooner, we could have been able to see an lyrical and erotic event.
It is a shame that Takako lost her way.
This is the first time I have been to Mikuriya's place...
If I remember correctly, you are Nagi-tan's younger sister...
We heard about the situation from Akiba-kun.
I was thinking of returning the KamaPure game that I borrowed from Akiba-kun.
But because he said that he suddenly had an errand related to you,
And you just barge into my house like that.
KamaPure is that thing at my part-time job the other day...
It is the game in which the cosplay was based on.
This is such an ordinary room, just like Mikuriya.
A room with absolutely no special traits resembles his artistic style.
Nagi, the president and the vice-president are here.
I rushed here because of you.
Sorry for making you come all this way.
Hey, this place is getting a bit cramped with the number of people increasing.
You can go home any time you want.
Tsugumi, you are such an idiot!
Nagi-sama, I have heard about yesterday's incident.
But you are not a person who should live the rest of your life in such a dark and cramped closet!
You have a duty to heal all the fanclub members with your cheerfulness and beauty!
You are the light of hope!
Since I have come all this way, you should come out!
Show me how you look in your home clothes!
You have showed your true intentions with that last sentence, Takako.
Well, this is a rare occurrence.
It could become hot news on the homepage.
Seriously, what did you come here for?
If you do not leave your house, you cannot grow taller!
I called him just in case,
but it seems he got the wrong idea.
Whether you are good at drawing or not is not important!
What is important is your passion!
Why are there so many people here?
I hope Akiba gets here soon...
It is really getting hot in here.
I am getting thirsty from the heat.
This place is more comfortable than I expected!
I should make this place my new shrine.
You have finally appeared, you little impurity!
Do not let it get away!
Even if you tell me that...
why is the all-star cast here?
I will explain the situation to you later.
Akiba-kun, I want to return this.
Akiba, hurry up and give me that thing.
What exactly is going on here?
It was on TV yesterday, was not it?
But she was taking a bath.
So I recorded a video for her.
But Nagi had already recorded something-cutie in that tape...
She got mad, saying that she had not watched it yet.
So that is why she shut herself up in the closet...
Yesterday was the climax of the Imposter-Cutie Chapter, after all.
Were you watching that program too?
There were episodes where I was impressed by the animation directors and special effects.
What is with that disinterested reaction of yours, when this is the subject of discussion for today's incident?
Akiba-kun brought Lolikko Cutie for you.
If you ask me, yesterday's episode was led by one of my favorite animation directors,
With his connections, a lot of original illustrators are gathered.
I do not have a DVD player in my house!
The best quality drawings have to be recorded with the best video quality.
I expected this, so I have also prepared a video!
Then you should have brought it out first.
In the past, there were many times I could not watch,
because my old man was watching baseball.
It might not have meant anything important to him,
but to me, it felt really unfair.
I wonder if I have done the same thing to you.
But I really thought you would be happy.
If someone did that for me, I thought I would have been very happy.
Even though it was a failure...
You are hungry, are not you?
I shall let bygones be bygones this time!
Do not ever come out of the closet!
You do not deserve to be called a member of the Lolikko!
How long are you going to keep staying with a visual figure like that?
The eel fillets are disappearing from the world!
I am late, I am late!
Did not the curse wear off?
The next episode of Kannagi is...!
Hey do not record over it!
